# TC20: DustDetected2
# Precondition: BoostMode
# Action: detect additional dust
# Expected: no visible state change. BoostMode and boost cleaning remain.
# Note: timer reset is an internal side effect and is not directly observable by the current CLI accessors.
power
start
dust
expect power on
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode boost
expect motor moving
dust
expect power on
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode boost
expect motor moving
expect motorForward true
exit
